			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3598948">
									

<p>Thank you! Looking for the event horizon where people give up their humanity in order to protect their existence is my favorite theme on the site. Mo does these terrible things <em>because</em> she's a good person, not in spite of it, which is what makes her intriguing to me. I haven't been able to prove to myself that she's wrong about any of it.</p>
<p>Looking back I saw how many stages of this you helped with, so thanks again for that. Looking forward to pushing deeper and deeper into whatever the heart of this thing turns out to be.</p>

							</div>

								
					
