			<div class="content" id="post-content-3599060">
									

<p>Wow, what a read!</p>
<p>*The* paragraph, *the* paragraph that the entire story builds toward, *the* paragraph where everything goes to hell&#8230;just <em>stunning</em> writing. Short bursts of chaos, one after another, but filled with beauty throughout.</p>
<p>A hell of a piece, this, and I can't wait to see, as you say, &quot;Mo&quot;.</p>

