    <div class="post-container" id="fpc-3599098">
                      
		<div class="post" id="post-3599098">
		<div class="long">
			<div class="head">
									<div class="options">
						<a href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,3599098)" class="btn btn-default btn-small btn-sm">Fold</a>
					</div>
								<div class="title" id="post-title-3599098">
																		
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(318209); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=318209&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610182119" alt="DrMagnus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=318209)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(318209); return false;" >DrMagnus</a></span> <span class="odate time_1506027077 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">21 Sep 2017 20:51</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3599098">
									

<p>So, I hesitated to make this post until I could articulate my feelings on it.</p>
<p>I feel the almost dream-like nature of the tale detracts heavily from the subject matter.</p>
<p>If Mo is supposed to be one of the test subjects, this works, though I'm still not a huge fan.</p>
<p>If Mo is not supposed to be one of the test subjects, the lack of solid description kinda pulls me out. I never really got engrossed in the story, it was all on the surface.</p>
<p>Beyond that, I felt some of the interactions felt implausible, and overall just didn't work for me.</p>
<p>What's frustrating, is this feels like 75% of something great, and there's just 25% missing. I never &quot;see&quot; where any of the characters are. They're just conversations, with some vague implications.</p>
<p>Thematically, it works, but it's definitely a frustrating read, personally.</p>

							</div>

								
					
